data.text:
2008-09: Despite the hard work she has put into rehab and trying to get back on the ice, Kennedy was unable to see ice time due to previous injuries.

2007-08: Did not see action due to injury.

2006-07: Saw action between the pipes in four contests, all of which were in conference ... notched wins in all four contests, including two shutouts ... recorded a 0.75 goals against average and a .946 save percentage ... earned her first collegiate win, making nine stops in a shutout victory over Union on Oct. 28 ... made a season-high 17 saves on Nov. 25 in a 3-2 win against Quinnipiac.

Before Dartmouth: Played goalie for the West Yellowhead AAA Timberwolves womenâ€™s midget hockey team in Southern Alberta ... earned a .910 save percentage and 2.87 goals against average in 1025 minutes ... attended Spruce Grove Jasper High School for junior and senior years ... attended Warner High School for her first two years.

Personal: Sarah Kennedy was born on April 14, 1988 ... daughter of Paul and Heather Kennedy ... has two sisters ... majoring in English literature ... this year Kennedy will be volunteering at local high schools and will be finishing up her teaching certification prior to graduation.
